{"tid":1926985,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［屌票黨] Boris 佛系防疫以後傳出要「楢山節考」 正要懲罰支持他的選民？","createTime":"2020-03-15T13:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T23:08:46.000Z","uid":78519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2afc22cbd5b0c72e987541e2ab17579eacdbe7","tid":1926985,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"Boris 佛系防疫以後傳出要「楢山節考」 正要懲罰支持他的選民？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;//其中在英國，首相府的首席科學家，甚至提出，多人染病，自然社會就有免疫力一說，嚇著不少人。<br />\n然後週末英國確診個案激增後，約翰遜似乎無法繼續佛系防疫，於是要宣布新政策了。<br />\n相傳期中一項是，要求70歲以上老人，在家或老人院，隔絕4個月。各大媒體政治記者得知爆料後，自然議論紛紛，負評也不斷。<br />\n<br />\nElderly could be quarantined for four months in 'wartime-style' mobilisation to combat coronavirus&hellip;<br />\nPeople over 70 will be instructed by the government to stay in strict isolation at home or in care homes for four&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.itv.com/news/2020-03-14/elderly-to-be-quarantined-for-four-months-in-wartime-style-mobilisation-to-combat-coronavirus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com%2Fnews%2F2020-03-14%2Felderly-to-be-quarantined-for-four-months-in-wartime-style-mobilisation-to-combat-coronavirus%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyVuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=8c0405c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.itv.com/news/2020-03-14/elderly-to-be-quarantined-for-four-months-in-wartime-style-mobilisation-to-combat-coronavirus/</a><br />\n見到這樣「楢山節考」的政策，我反而想到了去年大選的結果。Yougov 出口民調表示，65歲以上受訪者，64%支持保守黨。// &hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/gausee-寰雨膠事錄/boris-佛系防疫以後傳出要-楢山節考-正要懲罰支持他的選民-6b8fa5997d82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fgausee-%E5%AF%B0%E9%9B%A8%E8%86%A0%E4%BA%8B%E9%8C%84%2Fboris-%E4%BD%9B%E7%B3%BB%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%8C%E5%82%B3%E5%87%BA%E8%A6%81-%E6%A5%A2%E5%B1%B1%E7%AF%80%E8%80%83-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%81%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BB%96%E7%9A%84%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91-6b8fa5997d82&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyVuZLt